data.description: Discover a charming two-story gem on a corner lot with 4 bedrooms, including a main-level owner's suite. No HOA fees! Enjoy the convenience of being a stroll away from Goat Island Park, while relishing the tranquility of mature shade trees from your covered rocking chair front porch. This home features an encapsulated crawlspace, a cozy wood-burning fireplace, and an oversized deck in the backyard—perfect for entertaining. Experience comfort, convenience, and natural beauty in this desirable home.
